    "starterCode": "pen.up();\nfor(int i = 0; i < 12; i++){\n    pen.fd(80);\n    // 按i%3选颜色画圆\n    \n    pen.bk(80).rt(30);\n}",
    "solution": "pen.up();\nfor(int i = 0; i < 12; i++){\n    pen.fd(80);\n    if(i % 3 == 0) pen.oo(12, 1);\n    if(i % 3 == 1) pen.oo(12, 3);\n    if(i % 3 == 2) pen.oo(12, 2);\n    pen.bk(80).rt(30);\n}",
