    "solution": "pen.size(2);\nfor(int i=0; i<5; i++){\n    pen.c(9).fd(60);\n    pen.oo(20);\n    pen.up().bk(60).down();\n    pen.rt(72);\n}\npen.c(3).oo(15);",
