    "starterCode": "// 用取余和整除逐位提取数字并求和\n",
    "solution": "int n, sum;\ncin >> n;\nsum = 0;\nwhile(n > 0){\n    sum = sum + n % 10;\n    n = n / 10;\n}\ncout << sum;",
