    "starterCode": "// 勾股定理：c² = a² + b²，枚举 c 直到 c*c == c2\n",
    "solution": "int a, b, c2, c;\ncin >> a >> b;\nc2 = a*a + b*b;\nc = 0;\nwhile(c*c < c2) c = c + 1;\ncout << c;",
